NAME		cube.layer
SYNTAX		cube.layer <layer> [red green blue]
DESCRIPTION	Set all LEDs in a layer to the same colour. If the optional
		red, green and blue arguments are provided then that colour
		is used, otherwise the current working colour is used.
RETURN VALUE	None
EXAMPLES	Set all LEDs in layer 3 to the current working colour:
			cube.layer 3
		Set all LEDs in layer 3 to blue:
			cube.layer 3 0 0 63
SEE ALSO	cube.colour, cube.panel, cube.slice
